{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"final-quiz-10","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"期末冲刺","title":"期末冲刺练 第10题","difficulty":5,"tags":["规律","裂项"],"content":"观察下列式子：$a_1 = \\frac{3}{1 \\times 4} = \\frac{1}{1} - \\frac{1}{4}$；$a_2 = \\frac{3}{4 \\times 7} = \\frac{1}{4} - \\frac{1}{7}$；$a_3 = \\frac{3}{7 \\times 10} = \\frac{1}{7} - \\frac{1}{10}$；$a_4 = \\frac{3}{10 \\times 13} = \\frac{1}{10} - \\frac{1}{13}$；……\n\n按此规律，则 $a_n = $______(用含 $n$ 的式子表示，其中 $n$ 为正整数），并计算：$a_1 + a_2 + a_3 + ... + a_{100} = $______。","steps":[{"title":"解答","content":"$a_n = \\frac{3}{(3n-2)(3n+1)} = \\frac{1}{3n-2} - \\frac{1}{3n+1}$\n$a_1 + a_2 + ... + a_{100} = 1 - \\frac{1}{301} = \\frac{300}{301}$","formula":""}]},"id":"final-quiz-10"},"__N_SSG":true}